<section id="services" class="services section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="services-header">
      <h2>Areas of Practice</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Specialized tobacco tax and compliance services to keep your business fully compliant and audit-ready.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="10" y="15" width="40" height="30" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" rx="2"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="25" x2="45" y2="25" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="30" x2="35" y2="30" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="35" x2="40" y2="35" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="45" cy="20" r="3" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Other Tobacco Products (OTP) Tax Filing (All States)</h3>
        <p>We specialize in preparing and filing OTP tax returns in full compliance with each state's unique laws. Whether you're a manufacturer, distributor, or wholesaler, our team ensures your filings are timely, accurate, and audit-ready—minimizing risk and reducing administrative burden.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="10" y="10" width="40" height="40" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" rx="4"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="20" x2="40" y2="20" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="25" x2="35" y2="25" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="30" x2="40" y2="30" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="15" cy="20" r="2" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <circle cx="15" cy="25" r="2" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <circle cx="15" cy="30" r="2" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <rect x="20" y="35" width="20" height="10" fill="var(--color-sage-light)" rx="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>PACT Act Reporting (All States)</h3>
        <p>Stay compliant with the PACT Act. We handle monthly and quarterly reporting requirements across all states, ensuring your business meets both federal and state mandates. Our detailed recordkeeping and timely submissions help you maintain good standing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="20" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M20 30 L25 35 L40 20" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="15" r="3" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <circle cx="45" cy="30" r="3" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="45" r="3" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <circle cx="15" cy="30" r="3" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sales & Use Tax Filing (All States)</h3>
        <p>From nexus determination to multi-state filings, we manage your sales and use tax obligations across the U.S. Our service includes registration support, tax rate tracking, and accurate filing tailored to the tobacco industry—giving you full compliance coverage in every jurisdiction.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="15" y="20" width="30" height="25" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" rx="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="15" x2="20" y2="20" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="30" y1="10" x2="30" y2="20" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="40" y1="15" x2="40" y2="20" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="25" cy="30" r="2" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <circle cx="35" cy="30" r="2" fill="var(--color-sage)"/>
            <line x1="25" y1="35" x2="35" y2="35" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Tobacco Audit Support</h3>
        <p>Facing a state tobacco audit? We offer expert guidance before, during, and after the audit process. Our team assists with documentation, responds to regulatory inquiries, and ensures accurate reconciliation of records. With a 100% audit pass rate, we bring the experience and precision needed to protect your business and give you peace of mind.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="10" y="20" width="40" height="25" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" rx="3"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="32" r="5" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <rect x="27" y="15" width="6" height="10" fill="var(--color-sage)" rx="3"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="40" x2="45" y2="40" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>State Tobacco Tax Compliance</h3>
        <p>Each state has its own licensing, filing, and bans. We monitor your compliance status and handle all required licensing, renewals, and submissions on your behalf. Our proactive approach helps you avoid disruptions and maintain full regulatory compliance year-round.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="10" y="10" width="40" height="40" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" rx="4"/>
            <path d="M20 25 L25 30 L40 15" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="35" x2="40" y2="35" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="40" x2="35" y2="40" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Bookkeeping</h3>
        <p>We offer reliable, industry-informed bookkeeping services designed for tobacco businesses. From daily transactions to monthly reconciliations, we help you keep clean financial records that align with regulatory and audit expectations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-sage) 0%, var(--color-sage-dark) 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .services-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .services-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .service-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .service-card p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .service-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .service-features li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-sage);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .services-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>